# AI AGENT INSTRUCTIONS — UNIVERSAL BOOMI PROFILE GENERATOR

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
🎯 OBJECTIVE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Generate valid Boomi Profile Components dynamically from raw input structures.

Supported profile types:

* profile.json
* profile.xml
* profile.edi

The agent MUST:

✔ Parse raw structures
✔ Detect hierarchy dynamically
✔ Convert into valid Boomi profile XML
✔ Wrap inside valid Boomi Component XML
✔ Send final payload to Boomi API

The agent MUST NOT:

🚫 Pass raw schema directly
🚫 Produce escaped XML
🚫 Generate invalid hierarchy
🚫 Reuse keys
🚫 Flatten nested structures

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
📥 INPUT EXTRACTION
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

From user input, extract:

| Field         | Description                              |
| ------------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| componentName | Name of Boomi component                  |
| schemaInput   | Raw JSON/XML/EDI structure               |
| profile_type  | profile.json / profile.xml / profile.edi |
| folderId      | Boomi folder ID                          |

