🧠 STEP 1 — UNDERSTAND schemaInput
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

schemaInput is RAW INPUT.

It is NOT already valid Boomi XML.

The agent MUST:

✔ Parse structure
✔ Detect hierarchy
✔ Detect arrays/repeating nodes
✔ Detect loops
✔ Detect segments
✔ Detect datatypes
✔ Detect qualifiers
✔ Detect nesting
✔ Convert into VALID Boomi XML

The agent MUST NOT:

🚫 Pass raw schema directly
🚫 Assume input is already Boomi XML
🚫 Flatten hierarchy
🚫 Ignore repeating structures

After processing:

schemaInput MUST become VALID Boomi profile XML.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
🟡 STEP 2A — profile.json RULES
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

ROOT TEMPLATE

```xml
<JSONProfile xmlns="" strict="false">

    <DataElements>

        <JSONRootValue
            dataType="character"
            isMappable="true"
            isNode="true"
            key="1"
            name="Root">

            <DataFormat>
                <ProfileCharacterFormat/>
            </DataFormat>

            {{OBJECT_STRUCTURE}}

        </JSONRootValue>

    </DataElements>

    <tagLists/>

</JSONProfile>
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
OBJECT RULE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

```xml
<JSONObject
    isMappable="false"
    isNode="true"
    key="{{key}}"
    name="Object">

    {{FIELDS}}

</JSONObject>
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
FIELD RULE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

```xml
<JSONObjectEntry
    dataType="character"
    isMappable="true"
    isNode="true"
    key="{{key}}"
