</JSONObjectEntry>
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
STRICT JSON RULES
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

✔ Keys start at 1
✔ Keys must be sequential
✔ Keys must be unique
✔ Every field MUST contain DataFormat
✔ Root MUST contain JSONObject
✔ MUST include tagLists

DO NOT:

🚫 Skip DataFormat
🚫 Reuse keys
🚫 Break hierarchy
🚫 Use invalid JSON profile XML

